01:16:49.200 --> 01:16:50.361
Mr. President.

01:16:51.520 --> 01:16:52.760
Thanks, boss.

01:16:53.480 --> 01:16:54.641
Let me just check this is clear.

01:16:54.800 --> 01:16:55.847
Already clear.

01:16:58.120 --> 01:16:59.167
Okay.

01:16:59.600 --> 01:17:00.726
Fantastic.

